Power of Three:

SYMBOL :  NASDAQ
TIMEFRAME : 30MIN [ 8-9 PM IST ]
ENTRY TIMEFRAME: 1MIN

1) Determine the candle bias.
2) Wait for manipulation straight after the opening of candle.
3) Always buy below open and sell above open.'
4) In the manipulation phase: Entry Criteria :  Three bar reversal or outside reversal [ mostly accompanied with a wick candle ].
5) Stop loss : lowest low of the last 3-5 candles.
6) TP : Partials always at 1.5 , full at 2/2.5/3 : based on candle size and proximity of the wick to S/R.
